name: 尤利娅·雅莉姗·迪努
name_full: 尤利娅·雅莉姗·迪努 Iulia Alexandra Dinu
introduction: Iulia Alexandra Dinu is a Romanian film and theater actress .She was born on September 22, 1995 in Bucharest,Romania. She graduated from University of Theatrical Arts and Cinematography in 2017.In 2016, she plays first role in movie The Worthy.Other notable roles in One Step Behind the Seraphim (2017) .Play on the stage of the theater Clasic "Ioan Slavici" in Arad.
